<strong>B. What information do we collect?</strong> <br>

<p>As you access this website, certain information about you, such as Internet protocol (IP) addresses, your geographic location, the systems and programs used and the time spent, along with other similar information, may be stored on our servers or 3rd party servers like Google Analytics. Such stored information may not specifically identify you, but may be used by us for website traffic analysis or for such other purposes as we may deem appropriate. The information as detailed below is collected for us to be able to provide the services chosen by you and also to fulfill our legal obligations as well as our obligations towards third parties as per our User Agreement.</p>
<p><strong>"Personal Information"</strong> of User shall include the information shared by the User and collected by us for the following purposes:</p>
